snippet.title: END: Live Through It - Pre Alpha Teaser
snippet.description:
Official Teaser Trailer for Pre Alpha! 

● Play END: https://gamejolt.com/games/end/382993

♥ Support Tiko on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/endthegame

····················································································

● Itch.io: https://endthegame.itch.io/end
● Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/end/382993
● Twitter: https://twitter.com/TikosGames 
● Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/endlivethro...
● Join our Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ENDthegame/
● Discord: https://discord.gg/rxRNUYS

········································­­·······································­·­····

♪ "Crossing the Chasm" by Kevin Macleod

········································­­·······································­·­····

“END” is an upcoming low poly, zombie survival FPS & RTS game. You will fight, craft, and build to survive. Find & recruit other survivors, shape a community, and end those who stand in your way.

Start from the bottom, with nothing to your name, and no memory of what started the apocalypse. Find other survivors, to help you recreate what you remember about society, and rebuild it.

Raids, Rustlers, Animals, Zombies, you name it, the danger will be there. Will you live through the end?
